The 1998 Nottingham Open was an ATP tournament held in Nottingham, Great Britain. The tournament was held from June 15 to June 22. Jonas Bjrkman won his 2nd title of the year and the 16th of his career. Sweden Jonas Bjrkman defeated Zimbabwe Byron Black, 6-3, 6-2 United States Justin Gimelstob / South Africa Byron Talbot defeated Canada Sbastien Lareau / Canada Daniel Nestor, 7-5, 6-7, 6-4
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
